.TH "batadv_bla_add_claim" 9 "batadv_bla_add_claim" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
batadv_bla_add_claim \- Adds a claim in the claim hash
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" batadv_bla_add_claim
.BI "(struct batadv_priv *bat_priv "  ","
.BI "const u8 *mac "  ","
.BI "const unsigned short vid "  ","
.BI "struct batadv_bla_backbone_gw *backbone_gw "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bat_priv" 12
the bat priv with all the soft interface information
.IP "mac" 12
the mac address of the claim
.IP "vid" 12
the VLAN ID of the frame
.IP "backbone_gw" 12
the backbone gateway which claims it
